# File Upload, Smart Organization, Folder Management, Card UI, Workflow Automation & Notifications

Adding 5 major features to the CA Administration (DaM) platform: enhanced file upload with smart categorization (GST/ITR/Audit), admin folder management, card-based file UI, file review workflow automation, and a real-time notification system.

## Proposed Changes

### Backend — Database Schema

#### [MODIFY] [database.py](file:///d:/DaM/backend/database.py)

Add new tables and columns to support the features:

1. **`notifications` table** — stores real-time alerts for both CA and client
   - `id`, `user_id`, `type` (file_uploaded, file_reviewed, payment_received), `title`, `message`, `is_read`, `related_id`, `created_at`

2. **`files` table — new columns** (via migration):
   - `status` — `NVARCHAR(20) DEFAULT 'pending'` — tracks review workflow (pending → reviewed)
   - `reviewed_at` — `DATETIME2 NULL` — timestamp of when CA reviewed
   - `reviewed_by` — `INT NULL` — admin user who reviewed
   - `category` — `NVARCHAR(100) NULL` — smart category (GST, ITR, Audit, etc.)

3. **`folders` table — new columns** (via migration):
   - `parent_id` — `INT NULL` — enables nested folder structure (Year → Client → Type)
   - `created_by` — `INT NULL` — tracks who created (admin vs client)

