## Smart Category Mapping

The system will detect these CA-specific categories from filenames:

| Keywords | Category |
|----------|----------|
| gst, gstr, goods and service | GST |
| itr, income tax, tax return | ITR |
| audit, auditor | Audit |
| tds, tax deducted | TDS |
| balance sheet, bs | Balance Sheet |
| p&l, profit, loss | P&L |
| invoice, bill | Invoice |
| receipt, payment, voucher | Receipt |
| pan, aadhar, aadhaar, kyc | KYC |
| salary, payroll, payslip | Payroll |

